Koronets jumbo slices are my favorite in the neighborhood, especially the pepperoni. Now I'm an even a bigger fan as I ordered a special pie for Valentine's day and received an awesome heart shaped pizza.  Koronet were super easy to work with, accommodating, and delivered on time! Pizza arrived warm, cheesy, and delicious. We're very happy with our Valentine's Day Pizza and overall quality and taste of it all.  I was nervous as I only ordered a day in advance but they were super helpful. I even had to call and ask for the delivery to be an hour earlier than originally requested and they were so quick to accomodate. Definitely recommend and will order again soon! Thanks Koronet!

Super great jumbo pizza slices, awesome gyro sandwiches, very fast and reliable delivery.  One time my was order delayed. I only waited an hour which is not a big deal, most places will have you waiting about that long, but normally these guys deliver within twenty minutes so I called just to make sure nothing went wrong. I wasn’t even upset, but the man on the phone (I assume the manager/owner but I didn’t get his name) was extremely apologetic and friendly. He explained the situation and insisted on throwing in a free root beer.  That’s the type of behavior that bumps a place up from one of my local favorites to being my #1 go-to spot for ordering in. Highly recommended.
